milestones.description: Netravalkar and Malhotra's 55-run partnership is USA's highest for the 10th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 49 between Netravalkar and Hutchinson
Malhotra has broken the record for most sixes (16) in ODIs for USA, going past Steven Taylor's 10
Malhotra has broken the record for most runs in boundaries (112) in an innings in ODIs for USA, going past Steven Taylor's 70
Malhotra's 173 is the highest individual score in ODIs (for USA), surpassing Aaron Jones's 95
U.S.A.'s 134-run win against P.N.G. is the largest margin of victory in terms of runs in ODIs, beating 98-run win against U.A.E.
Malhotra has broken the record for most sixes in an innings (16) in ODIs for USA, going past Steven Taylor's 7
Netravalkar has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (15) for USA, going past Monank Patel
